  "description": "A Vocaloid producer known for the fast paced and unique lyrics in his songs and his unique characters such as [Aimaina-chan](https://vocadb.net/T/8644/aimaina-chan) and [Doushite-chan](https://vocadb.net/T/8643/doushite-chan).\nHis producer name comes from his first song [Hummed Song (Hana Uta)](https://vocadb.net/S/10493), which literally means \"nose song\".\n\n+ He collaborated with a cafe named [Shuminova](https://web.archive.org/web/*/https://shuminova.net) to create [Pinocchio-Tei](https://web.archive.org/web/*/https://shuminova.net/pinova).",
